	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_65275273"><p>From the point of view of climate change, Nuclear produces low CO2 relative to the amount of energy generated so it makes sense to call it "clean energy".  There are issues of waste, proliferation, and cost, but countries like France have shown that nuclear can be operated successfully.</p></div>
